## How to Use
1. Access the web app: [https://vicsanity623.github.io](https://vicsanity623.github.io)
2. Click "Choose File" to select an audio file (MP3/WAV/FLAC)
3. Select stem separation type (Vocals, Instruments, etc.)
4. Click "Separate Audio" to upload
5. Wait for server processing (progress bar will display)
6. Download ZIP file with separated stems when completed

## Supported Formats
- Input: MP3, WAV, FLAC (â‰¤100MB)
- Output: ZIP containing WAV stems (Demucs standard format)

